{"tid":2065450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無得食煙就係因為個正苦廢！","createTime":"2020-06-15T14:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:10:27.000Z","uid":209337,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"06b5be8afcb2a5c93977e37bd04941c939d1bd77","tid":2065450,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"自已食開煙，因為而家去唔到日本，我迫住食番點煙，講真，加熱煙好貴，又要食炒價。見到fd share 出黎，講得好岩，又一樣野正苦無理過我地煙民。明明立法左，就可以收下稅，又唔會有黑市。算啦，都買唔到煙食而家。so sad <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／／<br />\n<br />\n樣樣嘢都想管，偏偏唔肯將加熱煙納入框架，控煙政策原地踏步。<br />\n正如政府日前公布，香港去年的吸煙率出現微升0.2%，中年男性更增加3.4%，現行政策未能有效降低吸煙率，私煙反趨嚴重，而一刀切式全禁方案，只會令加熱煙用家改食傳統煙，造成惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n不少中年男性煙民已有多年吸煙習慣，要強行戒煙有一定難度，以煙害較傳統煙低嘅加熱煙作為逐步戒煙之過渡期，對佢哋嚟講係比強行戒煙較容易接受嘅方案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zQdQFO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zQdQFO.png&h=2aa3fc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/supportiqoshk/photos/a.190590258157291/661960321020280/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsupportiqoshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.190590258157291%2F661960321020280%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=b545b09b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/supportiqoshk/photos/a.190590258157291/661960321020280/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e01c07b912aa63309523f37bea63000637de66b1","tid":2065450,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"跟曱甴食冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n23kg"},{"pid":"554d0cbd8072fca9d95598b5473de49867fcda28","tid":2065450,"uid":63952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"室內冇得食煙真係痛哭🚬👎🏿"},{"pid":"4971ab63f5e2ba8f877011555960e3a8e81eeebf","tid":2065450,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T14: